    <stitle>NEWAY AD-123/246 DRIVE AXLE AIR SUSPENSIONS - REPLACE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>REPLACE</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="replace" graphiccount="0">
            <title>SHOCK ABSORBERS</title>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">It is recommended the vehicle be unloaded. Block vehicle to prevent rolling. Vehicle
                    must be at approximate air spring height to assure that tension is relieved on shocks.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Remove upper and lower mounting bolts and shock absorber.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Replace with correct shock absorber.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Tighten nuts to 110 ft-lbs. (149 N&#8226;m).</para>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
